{"tid":348510,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[哥哥]今夜，這月這正亮。","createTime":"2017-08-05T18:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T19:34:35.000Z","uid":51907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92ee6a33fb2916845ec43ecfefb4bc88d58e09d6","tid":348510,"uid":51907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:20:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Xfa4fCnDors\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXfa4fCnDors&d=jbB%2BFlsmArbzanvR1WaTsxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=02997713\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Xfa4fCnDors</a><br />\n<br />\n今夜 這月這正亮 但這愛意卻漸涼<br />\n抑壓著 不要心傷 現在難望見立場<br />\n一再望 這月更亮 但願我與你歲月長<br />\n可奈 心意一般堅剛 獨自默默維護理想<br />\n月亮光輝正耀放 我對你的愛一樣<br />\n日後倘若可再遇上 再與你愛歌低唱<br />\n默默再對望 但覺淚悄悄眼內藏<br />\n映著閃爍星光 仿佛默默問何日同步向<br />\n<br />\n一再望 這月更亮 但願我與你歲月長<br />\n可奈 心意一般堅剛 獨自默默維護理想<br />\n月亮光輝正耀放 我對你的愛一樣<br />\n日後倘若可再遇上 再與你愛歌低唱<br />\n默默再對望 但覺淚悄悄眼內藏<br />\n映著閃爍星光 仿佛默默問何日同步向<br />\n那答案有點勉強"},{"pid":"38725ae6d8cb60fec4cb2d6de3e54f37501ca671","tid":348510,"uid":51907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:22:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q83RUxe9t1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq83RUxe9t1k&d=jbB%2BFlsmArbzanvR1WaTsxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8802c9dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q83RUxe9t1k</a><br />\n<br />\nTOP TEN之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ac923b8be16cfc2bc07a74718e471ddb1f7467","tid":348510,"uid":51907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:24:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Axyzwt6-zbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAxyzwt6-zbo&d=jbB%2BFlsmArbzanvR1WaTsxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=2218c526\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Axyzwt6-zbo</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你太累 及時地道別沒有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438764ea0b46c108b9335b54a2dd0fb98c4bb906","tid"